Package me.sbasalaev.tybyco.descriptors

Class JvmMethodHandle

java.lang.Object
me.sbasalaev.tybyco.descriptors.JvmMethodHandle
public final class JvmMethodHandle extends Object
Reference to a method, constructor, field getter or setter. The kinds of this class are not in one-to-one correspondence with the tags of CONSTANT_MethodHandle_info structure. Instead, the correct tag is chosen by a CodeBlockBuilder based on a Java version, class kind and implied semantics.
See Also:
  • JVMS 4.4.8 The CONSTANT_MethodHandle_info Structure
